1:26:13.720 --> 1:26:15.549
so much, for being here.

1:26:16.930 --> 1:26:19.104
I'm glad we were able
to come to an agreement

1:26:19.139 --> 1:26:20.313
to support your work.

1:26:23.143 --> 1:26:24.386
- Support my work.

1:26:26.008 --> 1:26:27.458
That's surprising.

1:26:27.492 --> 1:26:30.599
I didn't know you'd taken
much interest in it before.

1:26:30.633 --> 1:26:33.188
- We only learned recently
how much good it can do.

1:26:37.675 --> 1:26:40.643
- Dr. Holmes, with respect,
may I ask you something?

1:26:41.920 --> 1:26:44.613
Why ignore my data?

1:26:44.647 --> 1:26:48.410
You read the report, you,
you know what happens.

1:26:48.444 --> 1:26:50.032
Klaralon doesn't work.

1:26:53.932 --> 1:26:55.693
- Let's say it doesn't work.

1:26:56.659 --> 1:26:58.143
What then?

1:26:58.178 --> 1:26:59.697
- Then why make it?

1:26:59.731 --> 1:27:01.250
- Because it will work.

1:27:01.285 --> 1:27:03.321
It will, in time.

1:27:03.356 --> 1:27:07.463
- You're a scientist, you
can't sign your name to a lie.

1:27:07.498 --> 1:27:08.637
- It's not a lie.

1:27:08.671 --> 1:27:09.983
It's a step on the path.

1:27:11.156 --> 1:27:14.263
I am here operating
in the real world,

1:27:14.298 --> 1:27:17.577
and if Klaralon is even
1% better than oxycodone,

1:27:17.611 --> 1:27:19.993
then that's 1% that
can change the world.

1:27:21.166 --> 1:27:23.168
You will never change
demand or behavior.

1:27:24.549 --> 1:27:26.827
But you will fund continued
research through these products

1:27:26.862 --> 1:27:28.173
and take a step closer

1:27:28.208 --> 1:27:29.865
to the ultimate
breakthrough that will come.

1:27:29.899 --> 1:27:31.729
- That's not my world.

1:27:31.763 --> 1:27:33.248
That's a cause.

1:27:33.282 --> 1:27:35.215
I don't deal in causes.

1:27:35.250 --> 1:27:36.768
- But somebody has to.
- I deal in science.

1:27:36.803 --> 1:27:37.942
I deal in truth.

1:27:37.976 --> 1:27:40.185
- And what precisely
is that truth?

1:27:40.220 --> 1:27:41.773
You think you get to
make that decision,

1:27:41.808 --> 1:27:43.499
along with all the
collateral damage

1:27:43.534 --> 1:27:45.087
it might bring with it?

1:27:45.121 --> 1:27:47.848
What about the millions
in pain who need this drug

1:27:47.883 --> 1:27:50.437
to ease their suffering
and use it legitimately?

1:27:51.783 --> 1:27:54.096
Should they be denied
care because you say so?

1:27:55.787 --> 1:27:58.169
- You're holding up
one animal study,

1:27:58.203 --> 1:28:00.309
one highly questionable study,

1:28:00.344 --> 1:28:01.759
while even you yourself know

1:28:01.793 --> 1:28:06.557
that 65% of these animal studies
don't translate to humans.

1:28:06.591 --> 1:28:10.457
And for that you wanna destroy
a chance at real relief?

1:28:11.665 --> 1:28:13.771
If that's not a cause,
I don't know what is.

1:28:26.473 --> 1:28:27.440
- I can't do it.

1:28:31.996 --> 1:28:33.066
I won't do it.

1:28:54.329 --> 1:28:57.401
[muffled rock music]

1:29:00.127 --> 1:29:00.956
- Jake.

1:29:01.991 --> 1:29:03.061
No Labatt tonight?

1:29:04.200 --> 1:29:05.029
- No.

1:29:05.995 --> 1:29:07.411
Just whiskey.

1:29:07.445 --> 1:29:08.515
- Takes all kinds.

1:29:11.000 --> 1:29:12.312
- We all set for tomorrow?

1:29:13.417 --> 1:29:16.420
- Of course we
are, what we said.

1:29:16.454 --> 1:29:17.317
- Good.

1:29:18.801 --> 1:29:20.493
So, where's the meet?

1:29:20.527 --> 1:29:23.772
- We still work out
a safe place for you.

1:29:23.806 --> 1:29:25.877
I'll tell you tomorrow, Correc'?

1:29:28.017 --> 1:29:29.122
- And you'll be there?

1:29:30.572 --> 1:29:31.780
'Cause I'll be there.

1:29:33.229 --> 1:29:35.128
And I'm not handing
all of my fucking money

1:29:35.162 --> 1:29:37.026
to somebody I never met before.

1:29:38.614 --> 1:29:40.789
- What, you worry I set you up?

1:29:40.823 --> 1:29:41.617
Is that it?

1:29:43.239 --> 1:29:44.827
Or maybe you set me up.

1:29:47.692 --> 1:29:49.453
It's a crazy business we choose.

1:29:51.316 --> 1:29:52.145
- Crazy.

1:29:54.492 --> 1:29:57.150
- I guess we'll
find out tomorrow.

1:29:57.184 --> 1:29:59.152
[laughing] Of course
I'll be there.

1:30:01.430 --> 1:30:03.121
You wanna eat something?

1:30:03.156 --> 1:30:05.158
We make a good steak here.

1:30:05.192 --> 1:30:06.021
- No.

1:30:06.953 --> 1:30:07.712
I'm going home.

1:30:07.747 --> 1:30:08.610
I'm going to bed.

1:30:10.646 --> 1:30:11.475
Tomorrow.

1:30:50.548 --> 1:30:51.549
Excuse me, miss.

1:30:51.584 --> 1:30:52.654
Can I help you?

1:30:52.688 --> 1:30:53.482
- No, I'm fine.

1:30:53.517 --> 1:30:55.001
Thank you.

1:30:55.035 --> 1:30:55.829
Oh.

1:30:55.864 --> 1:30:57.072
What?

1:30:57.106 --> 1:30:58.901
- Ms. Reimann, whatever
you're looking for,

1:30:58.936 --> 1:31:00.316
you are not gonna
find it in there.

1:31:00.351 --> 1:31:01.835
- What? [groans]

1:31:01.870 --> 1:31:04.320
- I suggest that you go home.

1:31:06.115 --> 1:31:07.703
Go all the way home.

1:31:08.566 --> 1:31:10.913
- How do you know who I am?

1:31:10.948 --> 1:31:12.432
- It doesn't matter.

1:31:12.467 --> 1:31:15.262
All that matters is that no
one wants to see you dead.

1:31:15.297 --> 1:31:16.125
Go home.

1:31:18.611 --> 1:31:20.302
- Okay. [breathing heavily]

1:31:20.336 --> 1:31:21.752
Oh, god.

1:31:21.786 --> 1:31:22.615
Oh, god.

1:31:35.559 --> 1:31:37.733
[sobbing]

1:31:45.776 --> 1:31:48.157
- In light of the
evidence presented

1:31:48.192 --> 1:31:50.988
and the university's
zero tolerance position

1:31:51.022 --> 1:31:52.368
on sexual harassment,

1:31:53.577 --> 1:31:55.820
the chair feels that
we have no choice

1:31:55.855 --> 1:31:59.065
but to recommend that Dr.
Brower's tenure be revoked

1:31:59.099 --> 1:32:00.584
and that his employment
at the university

1:32:00.618 --> 1:32:03.172
be terminated
effective immediately.

1:32:03.207 --> 1:32:04.449
All those in favor?

1:32:08.557 --> 1:32:09.385
Opposed?

1:32:11.146 --> 1:32:12.043
The ayes have it.

1:32:13.044 --> 1:32:14.874
This concludes our proceedings.

1:32:14.908 --> 1:32:17.980
[papers shuffling]

1:32:18.015 --> 1:32:21.915
[committee chattering quietly]

1:32:39.830 --> 1:32:42.660
[phone vibrating]

1:33:18.316 --> 1:33:21.734
[agents speaking French]

1:33:23.805 --> 1:33:28.154
- What did you just say?
